    • Method Detail

      • getRefSetMemberDeltas

        <D extends ComponentDelta> Collection<D> getRefSetMemberDeltas(IBranchPathMap branchPathMap,
                                                               String identifierConceptId)
        Returns a mapping between reference set member IDs and the changes of the corresponding components, which happened on the specified branch.
        Parameters:
        branchPathMap - the branch path map where the calculation is performed.
        identifierConceptId - identifier concept ID of a reference set which changes has to be tracked.
        Returns:
        a mapping between reference set member IDs and the corresponding changes on the branch.

      • promoteChanges

        @Nullable
Throwable promoteChanges(Collection<ComponentDelta> deltas,
                                    String identifierId,
                                    String userId,
                                    String commitComment)
        Promotes the reference set member changes given as a collection of component deltas. The collection of component deltas could be from different branches. The destination branch of the promotion process will be the parent branch of the component deltas.
        Parameters:
        deltas - the components to promote.
        identifierId - the reference set identifier concept ID.
        userId - unique user identifier.
        commitComment - commit comment for the promotion.
        Returns:
        a throwable indicating if any error, warning occurred while promoting the changes. Could be null.
